precis:
Amendment to the RADIATION EMITTING DEVICES revoking the present standard
on Extra-Oral Dental X-Ray Equipment and replacing it with a new one which
is compatible with internationally accepted standards and which reflects
the current state of technology in dental X-ray equipment design.
